TO ENCRYPT DATA AND FILE



	1. ansible-vault create creds.txt 

Set password 

Paste text

Save 

 cat creds.txt ( to view the encrypted file)

	2.  ansible-vault edit creds.txt  (To edit file encryted)
	3.  ansible-vault rekey creds.txt (To change vault password)
	4.  ansible-vault decrypt creds.txt ( To decrypt data)
cat creds.txt (to view unencrypted file)
	5. ansible-vault encrypt creds.txt (to encrypt)
	6. ansible-vault view creds.txt (To view plain txt without decrypting)



